              id="bff1d63c-2817-4ac1-a861-44c94888a70f" name="Manage Battery Safety"
              description="&lt;p>In order to ensure the safety of the battery and corresponding vehicle notify the vehicle control unit of safety issue that should send it to a lower current draw state.&lt;/p>&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p>Verify that a lower current draw state is underway by checking the high voltage signals current levels.&lt;/p>&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p>Take action to bypass cells if that capability exists&lt;/p>&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p>Present thermal request to cooling unit to maintain safety.&lt;/p>&#xA;"/>
